public class TaskRequestDto {

    @NotBlank
    private String title;

    private String description;

    @JsonFormat(pattern = "dd-MM-yyyy")
    private LocalDate dueDate;

    // no id, no status
}
ğŸ”§ 2. TaskResponseDto â€“ For responses
java
Copy
